{
  "stem": "13690.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we succeeded, in a way, that after a few months, the Polish family moved out from the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was plenty Jewish other homes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we occupied the four rooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one of my aunts-- and the house was really plundered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You could see that the plaster of the walls was removed and searching for-- for valuables.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because this was Zborowski house, and that they were looking for valuables.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was not in a hurry to go to look for these possessions, because I knew it's not there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they were just taking off the-- the mortar from the walls, the bricks were removed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they-- I'm sure that they found it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, one of my mother's sisters kept on insisting, 'Go down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Look.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know exactly in what corner it is.' And I went down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in a corner.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let's say this is the basement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the corner was there, and I started to dig.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I digged underneath the foundation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was put underneath the foundation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, underneath the foundation-- again, on the outside of the foundation, I couldn't dig from the outside, because there were the stairs there-- like the stairs, let's say, in this house.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were underneath.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I was digging, digging.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was water come in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I could not find it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I could not find anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I got tired, I came back up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Went again down and digged again a little bit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Again, couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "One day, my aunt was really persistent, and she said, 'I want you to continue.' And I continued, I continued.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And sure enough, I found it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was 10 boxes with gold and all kind of precious metal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the-- it was actually-- the 10 boxes were rusted.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
